<title>BRAZIL: FORECAST - Individual survey of Brazilian indicators.</title>
<headline>FORECAST - Individual survey of Brazilian indicators.</headline>
<dateline>SAO PAULO 1996-08-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following are individual economic forecasts collected by Reuters from the offices of eight brokerages and research firms in Sao Paulo and Rio de Janeiro. The survey is updated twice monthly after the government statistical institute IBGE releases industrial activity figures early in the month and the trade balance later in the month.</p>
<p>	 *****Brazil Individual Economic Forecasts*****</p>
<p>----------------------------------------------------------------</p>
<p>PERIOD	     August	  August		 August</p>
<p>INDICATOR	CPI (Fipe)  PPI (IPA-M/FGV)   Infltn (IGP-M/FGV)</p>
<p>----------------------------------------------------------------</p>
<p>Banco da Bahia  0.70 pct	 na		   0.25 pct</p>
<p>Banco de Boston 0.62 pct	 na		   na</p>
<p>Fonte Cindam    0.45 pct	 0.17 pct	   0.25 pct</p>
<p>JP Morgan	 0.70 pct	 na		   0.50 pct</p>
<p>Matrix	    0.65 pct	 0.15 pct	   0.25 pct</p>
<p>MCM Consultores 0.85 pct	 0.31 pct	   0.30 pct</p>
<p>Trend	     0.75 pct	 0.01 pct	   0.15 pct</p>
<p>Unibanco	  0.76 pct	 0.40 pct	   0.42 pct</p>
<p>---------------------------------------------------------------</p>
